snippet: For Mr. Walker, the budget fight was an unwanted struggle in a year when nearly everyone in Madison was intensely aware of the stakes given his presidential aspirations.
abstract: Wisconsin Gov Scott Walker signs $72 billion state budget hours before announcing his 2016 presidential bid; budget includes over 100 changes made using line-by-line veto power and is opposed by members of both parties in legislature.
lead_paragraph: For Mr. Walker, the budget fight was an unwanted struggle in a year when nearly everyone in Madison was intensely aware of the stakes given his presidential aspirations.

headline.main: Stakes High, Scott Walker Signs Wisconsin Budget
headline.print_headline: Stakes High, Walker Signs Wisconsin Budget
